{"rule_id": "72e6d830-a0a1-4e85-9906-baed9569e2a1", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "Ozon 全球平台禁售商品", "summary": "烟草、电子烟及配件、酒类、未在俄认证的药品/维生素/膳食补充剂，以及钞票、证券、贵金属、身份证件等属于平台禁售品。", "content": "- 禁售：烟草制品、水烟、电子烟及尼古丁消费类设备及配件。\n- 禁售：酒精饮料，以及俄罗斯法律禁止远程销售或需特殊许可/牌照的商品。\n- 禁售：未取得俄罗斯认证的药品、维生素和膳食补充剂。\n- 禁售：含毒品/精神药物形象或内容、宣扬纳粹/极端主义标志、宣传非传统性关系的商品。\n- 禁售：钞票、有价证券、贵金属和身份证件。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/product-rules/special-categories/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["禁售品", "合规", "Ozon"]}
{"rule_id": "4267060a-97e1-412d-b400-740e9f855e4b", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "受限类目商品须凭证销售", "summary": "烟花、医疗器械等受限商品需满足特定条件并提供俄方注册证或合格证才可销售。", "content": "- 烟花：仅允许危险等级不高于 III 级，且需特殊存储与运输条件，并提供合格证书（Certificate of Conformity）。\n- 医疗器械：须已通过俄罗斯国家注册并持有俄罗斯境内的注册证。\n- 待核验：上述等级/证件要求为二手概括，具体阈值与适用范围以官方原文为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/product-rules/special-categories/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["受限品", "证书", "烟花", "医疗器械"]}
{"rule_id": "8d816009-74df-4377-9cbf-f47d8d222de2", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "Ozon 销售佣金与履约方案差异", "summary": "销售佣金按账户内售价分档计费；采用 FBP 方案比自有仓库销售少付 1% 佣金，仓储费另付给合作仓。", "content": "- 销售佣金依据卖家账户中设置的售价计费，并按价格区间适用不同费率（约：≤1500 卢布、1501–5000 卢布、>5000 卢布三档）。\n- FBP 方案下，向 Ozon 支付的佣金比自有仓库销售低 1%；仓储服务费直接支付给合作仓。\n- 待核验：具体费率与价格分档以官方佣金表为准（费率随类目及更新日期变动）。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/commissions/ozon-fees/commissions/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["佣金", "费用", "FBP"]}
{"rule_id": "5cc66604-fed6-4f0c-93ba-e9ffdbfa6167", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "卖家费用结构总览", "summary": "Ozon 卖家成本由销售佣金、物流/履约服务费及其他增值服务费构成。", "content": "- 卖家费用主要包括：销售佣金、履约与物流相关费用、以及其他服务费。\n- 不同履约方案（rFBS/FBP）对应的费用项与计费方式不同，应结合方案规划成本。\n- 详细费率请以官方费用结构页与佣金表为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/commissions/ozon-fees/seller-expenses-structure/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["费用结构", "成本", "Ozon"]}
{"rule_id": "f2d1a0f4-1714-442c-ba1d-d931e2ac9d13", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "realFBS（rFBS）卖家自履约方案", "summary": "rFBS 方案下卖家自行负责商品的存储与配送，自行拣货打包并自送或经集成物流服务发货。", "content": "- rFBS（Real Fulfillment by Seller）：卖家负责商品的存储与配送。\n- 订单提交并被卖家接收后，由卖家自行拣货、打包。\n- 卖家可自行配送，或通过集成的物流服务完成交付。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/fulfillment/rfbs/fulfillment-by-seller/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["rFBS", "自履约", "物流"]}
{"rule_id": "99d60389-3302-47e9-8603-25ccae1ead8e", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "FBP 合作仓履约方案", "summary": "FBP 方案下卖家将商品入仓 Ozon 合作伙伴仓库（如中国境内），由 Ozon 与合作方代为拣货、打包、贴标和发货。", "content": "- FBP（Fulfillment by Partner）：卖家可将商品放置于 Ozon 合作伙伴仓库（含中国境内仓）。\n- Ozon 与合作方代卖家完成拣货、打包、贴标与发货。\n- 该方案佣金比自有仓库销售低 1%，仓储费直接支付给合作仓。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/fulfillment/fbp/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["FBP", "合作仓", "履约"]}
{"rule_id": "d728eb1d-473a-4114-aa1a-1b2559ab2b20", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "订单包装要求", "summary": "包装须密闭不可触及内容物、完好干燥洁净；按商品特性防护，易碎品须贴标。", "content": "- 包装内容物不可被外部触及，包装须完好、干燥、洁净。\n- 应按商品特性包装，避免货物破损或损坏其他货件；突出部件单独包装，空隙用纸张填充防止内部移动。\n- 易碎商品须加贴“易碎，请勿摔落”标识。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/fulfillment/rfbs/logistic-settings/order-packaging-requirements/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["包装", "易碎品", "物流"]}
{"rule_id": "0e7adcdd-d3f4-43d9-9a2c-79be48b0274d", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "FBP 标签打印与粘贴要求", "summary": "标签须自卖家后台打印，用热敏/热转印打印机整张打印，贴于包裹最大面且无翘边；2026-01-14 起尺寸由 12×7.5cm 改为 4×5.8cm。", "content": "- 标签从 Ozon 个人账户打印，原尺寸 12×7.5 cm；自 2026-01-14 起改为 4×5.8 cm。\n- 须用热敏或热转印打印机，表面哑光或半光；整张打印（不可撕裂或多片拼接）。\n- 贴于包裹最大面，完整粘贴、无缝隙或翘起。\n- 待核验：尺寸切换日期与具体规格以官方原文为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/fulfillment/rfbs/logistic-settings/order-packaging-requirements/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["标签", "贴标", "FBP"]}
{"rule_id": "52bdf477-1684-41d8-b99e-4d273c12a7c2", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "合格商品退货条件与流程", "summary": "外观、封条、标签完好且无使用痕迹的合格商品方可退货；客户提交退货申请并附图，24 小时内受理，批准后须在期限内寄回。", "content": "- 合格商品退货须满足：外观、出厂封条与标签完好、无使用痕迹、原包装未损、消费属性保留。\n- 客户创建退货申请，需说明退货原因并附商品图片；申请约 24 小时内受理。\n- 客户须在申请批准后约 4 天内寄回；可送至 Ozon 自提点或寄至仓库设置中指定地址。\n- 待核验：受理与寄回时限为二手概括，以官方原文为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/fulfillment/rfbs/refunds/returns-3pl/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["退货", "退款", "rFBS"]}
{"rule_id": "4d9bb8bd-3aaf-49da-869c-453db2cdecb1", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退货卖家决策与自动批准规则", "summary": "卖家须在期限内对退货作出决定；逾期未处理将自动批准并向客户退款。", "content": "- 卖家有约 1 个日历日对退货作出决定。\n- 若收到退货后约 7 个日历日内卖家仍未作决定，申请将自动批准，客户获得退款。\n- 退款约在 10 天内退至客户余额；客户全额退款后 Ozon 会向卖家返还其 Ozon 佣金。\n- 待核验：上述天数为二手概括，以官方原文为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/fulfillment/rfbs/refunds/money/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["退货", "自动批准", "退款时限"]}
{"rule_id": "1cd31f0d-791f-4049-8ab6-ac2fed8afb6f", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "退货、未取件与取消产生的费用", "summary": "客户退货、未赎回订单及取消会对卖家产生相关费用。", "content": "- 客户退货、未取件（未赎回）订单及订单取消，均可能对卖家产生费用。\n- 该类费用与履约方案相关，应纳入成本测算。\n- 具体计费项与金额以官方费用页为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/commissions/ozon-fees/returns-expenses/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["退货费用", "未取件", "取消"]}
{"rule_id": "c074d7ca-6d08-4d08-8562-6908ce0a2cc1", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "账户/商品/仓库封禁原因", "summary": "违反平台规则、欠缴服务费、同一税号开设过多账户或账户长期不活跃，均可能导致封禁。", "content": "- 违反平台规则可导致账户、商品或仓库被封禁。\n- 典型原因：拖欠 Ozon 服务费；同一税号（TIN）/营业执照开设超过 6 个账户。\n- 账户不活跃亦会被封：接受协议后约 45 天仍未上传商品，或上传商品后约 60 天仍无首单。\n- 待核验：账户数量与不活跃天数为二手概括，以官方原文为准。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/ratings/ban/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["封禁", "账户健康", "合规"]}
{"rule_id": "f5f4366a-c9a1-4583-a4ae-bbb20193480b", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "服务质量指标超限封禁", "summary": "服务质量指标超过最大允许值（如售假、超期发货、高取消率、高瑕疵退货率）将导致商品被封。", "content": "- 服务质量指标超过最大允许值时，Ozon 会封禁相关商品。\n- 触发因素包括：销售劣质或假冒商品、违反订单包装与发货时限。\n- 高订单取消率、高瑕疵退货率亦计入指标。\n- 待核验：各指标具体阈值以官方质量指标页为准。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/launch/quality-assurance/quality-metrics/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["质量指标", "封禁", "售假"]}
{"rule_id": "aaea19de-e101-43d8-b2f6-2a2db0c6a6d5", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "低评分商品持续销售致永久封号", "summary": "账户被暂停期间应整改低评分商品；若继续销售低评分商品，Ozon 可能永久封禁账户。", "content": "- 账户被暂停期间，卖家应分析并整改商品。\n- 若持续销售低评分商品，Ozon 可能永久封禁账户。\n- 建议优先处理低评分与高退货商品以恢复账户。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/ratings/product-rate/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["商品评分", "永久封禁", "处罚"]}
{"rule_id": "81112323-3537-46db-9ae6-300d632787b7", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "商品图片要求", "summary": "附加图片不超过 29 张，须与名称描述相符、无水印；食品须含配料表图；按文件名编号可控制展示顺序。", "content": "- 附加图片最多 29 张，须与商品名称和描述一致，且无水印。\n- 食品类若描述中无配料表，须提供含配料清单的图片。\n- 如需按顺序上传，可对文件名编号（如 1、2、3 或 product1、product2…）。\n- 待核验：图片数量上限以官方图片要求页为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/products/requirements/media/image-requirements/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["图片", "Listing", "商品卡"]}
{"rule_id": "612e07a5-4a21-42e1-8b9b-4d438b9d725b", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "商品描述内容规范", "summary": "描述可自由撰写但须合规：禁止联系方式、过量字符堆砌，及“仿品/复制/1:1/原单”等暗示售假的措辞。", "content": "- 描述可自由撰写，但应避免与商品不符的搜索词堆砌。\n- 禁止包含电话、网址、社交账号等联系方式。\n- 避免大量无意义字符堆砌（如某些中/日文商品的字符堆砌）。\n- 禁止使用“analog/fake/copy/replica/1:1/based on/original/authentic”等措辞——平台禁止销售仿冒品。\n- 使用 rich-content（图文/视频）可在内容评分中加 20 分。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/products/requirements/product-description/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["描述", "Listing", "禁用词"]}
{"rule_id": "276be4bd-a9c9-4f7b-b385-edd20d2ea629", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "品牌资质与销售授权要求", "summary": "高仿风险品牌需通过品牌文件审核后才会打标；非从权利人处采购的，须凭与权利人签订的许可协议/授权信证明销售权。", "content": "- Ozon 品牌规则适用于在俄罗斯或国际知识产权体系注册商标/品牌的品牌；在 Ozon 注册品牌不等于取得商标权。\n- 对常被仿冒的热门品牌，须通过品牌文件审核后 Ozon 才会打标。\n- 若直接从权利人或经其同意的渠道购入，可无需品牌方额外授权销售。\n- 若非从权利人且未经其同意购入，须凭与权利人签订的许可协议证明使用权，并提供授权/豁免信。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/documents/brand/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["知识产权", "品牌证书", "授权"]}
{"rule_id": "722cf0df-95b9-4a4d-baec-747029c6c7cf", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "假冒商品禁售与举报", "summary": "销售假冒或禁售商品是封号原因；发现他人非法销售品牌商品可联系支持团队举报并隐藏其商品页。", "content": "- 销售假冒或禁售商品是卖家账户被封禁的原因之一。\n- 如认为他人在 Ozon 非法销售品牌商品（疑似假冒/未授权），可联系支持团队。\n- 举报后相关商品可被隐藏其商品详情页，使客户不可见。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/documents/brand/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["假冒", "举报", "知识产权"]}
{"rule_id": "79287ab1-2177-4bd0-8bae-0095f7a4ca74", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "商品质量证书提供义务", "summary": "不受限商品可先上架，但 Ozon 可随时索证；卖家须在收到请求后约 3 个工作日内提供，否则相关商品销售可被暂停。", "content": "- 不受限商品可不预先上传质量证书直接销售，但 Ozon 可随时要求提供。\n- 卖家须在收到请求后约 3 个工作日内提交文件；逾期未交，Ozon 有权暂停相关商品销售。\n- 质量由合格声明、合格证书、自愿合格证书或豁免信证明，提交后由质控部门审核（核对签章清晰度与一致性）。\n- 待核验：提交时限以官方原文为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/products/documents/quality-certificate/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["资质", "质量证书", "类目"]}
{"rule_id": "c0513d29-862b-4323-8888-f00034bc21a6", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "Ozon 推广工具与计费", "summary": "提供 Stencils、搜索结果推广、品牌货架、展示广告等工具；按曝光或按单计费，按单推广每单最低约 5 卢布。", "content": "- 主要推广工具：Stencils（搜索/类目/详情页等位置推广，自动设置、按曝光计费）、搜索结果推广（按推广商品成交计费）、品牌货架、展示广告、营销请求。\n- 推广广告默认日预算约 500 卢布/天，最低费率约 150 卢布/千次曝光（1 卢布步进）。\n- 按单推广每单最低约 5 卢布，费率按推广商品类目固定。\n- 待核验：上述金额为二手概括，以官方推广页为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/promotion/product-promotions/product-promotion/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["广告", "推广", "计费"]}
{"rule_id": "85895879-5c5c-4b22-80a5-c6f17c097ea3", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "payments", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "结算货币与回款规则", "summary": "注册时选定结算货币（中国为 CNY），选定后不可更改；仅“已送达”订单计入回款，达到门槛才付款。", "content": "- 结算货币在注册时选定，多数国家为 USD/RUB，中国可选 CNY；账户建立后不可再更改。\n- 仅“Delivered（已送达）”状态订单计入付款；账户金额达到门槛才转账，未达则顺延至下一付款日。\n- 自 2024-01-01 起，USD 款项按俄央行交叉汇率折算为 CNY；中国卖家不支持银行电汇方式。\n- 待核验：货币与日期细节以官方结算页为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/accounting/receiving-payments/payment-currency/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["结算货币", "回款", "支付"]}
{"rule_id": "0e66875d-725e-4413-899d-b81548fc3eb1", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "跨境 VAT 与关税处理", "summary": "若 Ozon 须就所售商品缴纳 VAT，由客户在售价之外支付税款；包裹超免税额时由客户承担关税，并需随附发票通关。", "content": "- VAT：若 Ozon 须就卖家通过平台所售商品缴纳 VAT 或类似税，客户在售价之外支付该税款，税款汇至 Ozon 账户并上缴相应国家财政。\n- 关税：包裹价值低于 1000 欧元且重量不超过 31 kg 通常免征关税；超限部分由客户缴纳，按超额 15% 或每超 1kg 收 2 欧元（取较高者）。\n- 通关：随货发票有助于通关，须填写 HS Code（GTIP）等信息；卖家须在交货时向运营方提交发票、规格、运输与装箱单等外贸单据。\n- 待核验：免税额、税率及单据要求随国别/时间变动，以官方原文为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://docs.ozon.ru/global/en/prices/customs-duties/", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["VAT", "关税", "税务合规"]}
